tool_description: Unlock the Power of YouTube with the Private API! Gain exclusive access to YouTube's advanced features and data, enabling seamless integration into your applications. Customize interactions, retrieve in-depth analytics, and create personalized experiences to elevate your content strategy. The Private API offers unparalleled control and insights for developers looking to enhance their YouTube-related projects.
name: YouTube Private
title: YouTube Private

api_list.name: Get Channel Videos
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://youtube-private.p.rapidapi.com/get-channel-videos"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "youtube-private.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.post(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
